<li><a href="http://download.microsoft.com/download/1/1/a/11ac6505-e4c0-4e05-987c-6f1d31855cd2/Identity-Selector-Interop-Profile-v1.pdf" class="external text" title="http://download.microsoft.com/download/1/1/a/11ac6505-e4c0-4e05-987c-6f1d31855cd2/Identity-Selector-Interop-Profile-v1.pdf" rel="nofollow">Identity Selector Interoperability Profile</a>, Arun Nanda, April 2007.</li>
<li><a href="http://download.microsoft.com/download/1/1/a/11ac6505-e4c0-4e05-987c-6f1d31855cd2/Identity-Selector-Interop-Profile-v1-Guide.pdf" class="external text" title="http://download.microsoft.com/download/1/1/a/11ac6505-e4c0-4e05-987c-6f1d31855cd2/Identity-Selector-Interop-Profile-v1-Guide.pdf" rel="nofollow">An Implementer's Guide to the Identity Selector Interoperability Profile V1.0</a>, Microsoft Corporation and Ping Identity Corporation, April 2007.</li>
<li><a href="http://download.microsoft.com/download/1/1/a/11ac6505-e4c0-4e05-987c-6f1d31855cd2/Identity-Selector-Interop-Profile-v1-Web-Guide.pdf" class="external text" title="http://download.microsoft.com/download/1/1/a/11ac6505-e4c0-4e05-987c-6f1d31855cd2/Identity-Selector-Interop-Profile-v1-Web-Guide.pdf" rel="nofollow">A Guide to Using the Identity Selector Interoperability Profile V1.0 within Web Applications and Browsers</a>, Michael B. Jones, April 2007.</li>
<li><a href="http://research.microsoft.com/~mbj/papers/Identity_Metasystem_Design_Rationale.pdf" class="external text" title="http://research.microsoft.com/~mbj/papers/Identity_Metasystem_Design_Rationale.pdf" rel="nofollow">Design Rationale behind the Identity Metasystem Architecture</a>, Kim Cameron and Michael B. Jones, January 2006.</li>
<li><a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=98051" class="external text" title="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=98051" rel="nofollow">Patterns for Supporting Information Cards at Web Sites: Personal Cards for Sign up and Signing In</a>, Bill Barnes, Garrett Serack, and James Causey, August 2007.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.microsoft.com/interop/osp/" class="external text" title="http://www.microsoft.com/interop/osp/" rel="nofollow">Microsoft Open Specification Promise</a>, May 2007.</li>
<li><a href="http://www-03.ibm.com/linux/opensource/ispinfo.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www-03.ibm.com/linux/opensource/ispinfo.shtml" rel="nofollow">IBM Interoperability Specifications Pledge</a>, July 2007.</li>
</ul>
